{
    "name": "Superstitious Mercenary",
    "type": "npc",
    "sections": [
        {
            "name": "Description",
            "html": "Some mercenaries believe their survival has less to do with skill and more to do with their ability to gain the gods\u2019 favor."
        },
        {
            "name": "Corwyn Klas",
            "type": "section",
            "html": "When between jobs, Corwyn faithfully maintains his clothes, armor, and weapons, but once hired, he stops keeping up his appearance and grows more disheveled as the days pass.<br/><br/>Corwyn fears the supernatural, and keeps a holy symbol with him at all times. He blows his wages on worthless talismans sold with promises to work against fiends and spirits."
        }
    ],
